{"tid":2359562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民車場外默哀 群警阻獻花","createTime":"2021-01-09T04:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T04:16:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20211d06a32d2ed1065d0a6e5a6997329c13a201","tid":2359562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/4DM3KXNTSVHEPEMMCDF6LYNER4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2F4DM3KXNTSVHEPEMMCDF6LYNER4%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=117f971a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210109%2F4DM3KXNTSVHEPEMMCDF6LYNER4%2F&h=1dc2268c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210109/4DM3KXNTSVHEPEMMCDF6LYNER4/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民車場外默哀 群警阻獻花<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日是科大學生周梓樂在將軍澳尚德邨停車場墮斃第14個月，昨日中午過後已有市民自發到尚德邨停車場獻花悼念，另外入夜後近20名市民響應網民號召於晚上8時09分，即周梓樂宣告死亡一刻，冒着8℃低溫在停車場外默站哀悼。不過哀悼活動卻觸動政府神經。警方如臨大敵，下午起多部警車到場，數十警員在尚德邨停車場對出十字路口（尚十）一帶佈防，並清走悼念物品，但仍有大批市民冒着寒風，前來悼念。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：官供三選項 可揀非法被殺  須無合理疑點 陪審團商六小時無果今續議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Tqh5rEB8mE9_0n-wecqLVQ6esLY=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PQJIJGPCZJAJVDJX7BOOE5AHPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTqh5rEB8mE9_0n-wecqLVQ6esLY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPQJIJGPCZJAJVDJX7BOOE5AHPU.jpg&h=0dfafa11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■社工呂智恆（右）昨晚為周梓樂祈禱，其間被大批警員監視。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呂智恆祈禱遭包圍監視<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午，有多名市民到「尚十」祭壇位置，及尚德停車場二樓及三樓，擺放鮮花及燃點蠟燭悼念，並放下「香港人加油」的紙卡。至於周梓樂墮樓位置，昨日已被圍封白布。<br />\n<br />\n至下午5時許，四部警車響着警號抵達「尚十」，30多名軍裝警分兵多路，分別在尚德邨停車場內外巡邏戒備，並登上停車場各層巡視。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：建議不可涉警調查甩漏<br />\n<br />\n入夜後，警方在「尚十」外擺放易拉架，警告市民切勿聚集。當時近20名市民冒着寒風到來擺放鮮花悼念，卻遭旁邊監視警員阻止。至晚上8時，警力再度加強，警員更截查旁觀的市民及在現場拉起封鎖線，引起市民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n社工呂智恆到場為周梓樂祈禱，多名警員更將他包圍監視；其間一名女子擺放寫有「別讓真相沉沒」紙牌，二人同被警告，其後才獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/STUNfa180xcTCt8eRZZcle3EXnQ=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZN3TY2V4UBAJVH2PEF5YRQSHEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSTUNfa180xcTCt8eRZZcle3EXnQ%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZN3TY2V4UBAJVH2PEF5YRQSHEQ.jpg&h=33e1a434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有人在停車場內擺放鮮花及點蠟燭悼念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gdc6PWkBnPbF56kig5SVPm0Txp0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5O7OT3EHB5CHPCL4QUHSGD6H6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fgdc6PWkBnPbF56kig5SVPm0Txp0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5O7OT3EHB5CHPCL4QUHSGD6H6U.jpg&h=0452c5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員在尚德邨停車場外截查在場市民。"}]}